would be dangerous to you?

306
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:24,860
I'll take a hard truth
over a nice lie any day.

307
00:24:30,480 --> 00:24:33,300
We never really established this,

308
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:36,940
'cause when we met...

