marriage, our children...

335
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:13,740
it's all...

336
00:26:13,820 --> 00:26:15,820
tied up in a...

337
00:26:15,860 --> 00:26:18,656
dead boy and a missin' girl.

338
00:26:26,989 --> 00:26:29,114
