347
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:36,650
What the fuck did you
say, you little midget?

348
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:38,698
See, I always wondered,

349
00:27:38,781 --> 00:27:41,440
all this butt-faced
human pieces of garbage

350
00:27:41,460 --> 00:27:43,280
