504
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:21,300
well, the father, we'd just
have to figure somethin' out.

505
00:40:21,489 --> 00:40:24,156
But... eh...

506
00:40:24,230 --> 00:40:25,920
Miss Isabel, she...

507
00:40:26,070 --> 00:40:28,080
